{
    "publish_date": "2013-10-08T16:00:59.000Z", 
    "score": 6.163404171391943e-05, 
    "video_length": "PT4M8S", 
    "captions": [
        {
            "text": "Palms sweaty,", 
            "dur": "1.036", 
            "start": "7.809"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "heart racing,", 
            "dur": "0.71", 
            "start": "8.845"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "stomach in knots.", 
            "dur": "1.45", 
            "start": "9.555"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You can&#39;t cry for help.", 
            "dur": "1.375", 
            "start": "11.528"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Not only is your throat too tight to breathe,", 
            "dur": "1.878", 
            "start": "12.903"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but it&#39;d be so embarrassing.", 
            "dur": "2.143", 
            "start": "14.781"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "No, you aren&#39;t being stalked by a monster,", 
            "dur": "2.169", 
            "start": "16.924"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you&#39;re speaking in public,", 
            "dur": "1.717", 
            "start": "20.616"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "a fate some deem worse than death.", 
            "dur": "2.766", 
            "start": "22.333"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "See, when you&#39;re dead, you feel nothing;", 
            "dur": "1.761", 
            "start": "25.099"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "at a podium, you feel stage fright.", 
            "dur": "2.373", 
            "start": "26.86"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But at some point we&#39;ve all had to communicate", 
            "dur": "2.037", 
            "start": "32.309"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "in front of people,", 
            "dur": "1.001", 
            "start": "34.346"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "so you have to try and overcome it.", 
            "dur": "2.141", 
            "start": "35.347"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "To start, understand what stage fright is.", 
            "dur": "3.221", 
            "start": "37.488"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Humans, social animals that we are,", 
            "dur": "2.169", 
            "start": "40.709"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "are wired to worry about reputation.", 
            "dur": "2.099", 
            "start": "42.878"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Public speaking can threaten it.", 
            "dur": "1.742", 
            "start": "44.977"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Before a speech, you fret,", 
            "dur": "2.146", 
            "start": "46.719"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;What if people think I&#39;m awful and I&#39;m an idiot?&quot;", 
            "dur": "2.826", 
            "start": "48.865"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "That fear of being seen as an awful idiot", 
            "dur": "1.88", 
            "start": "51.691"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is a threat reaction", 
            "dur": "1.23", 
            "start": "53.571"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "from a primitive part of your brain", 
            "dur": "1.408", 
            "start": "54.801"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that&#39;s very hard to control.", 
            "dur": "2.002", 
            "start": "56.209"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s the fight or flight response,", 
            "dur": "1.584", 
            "start": "58.211"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "a self-protective process seen in a range of animals,", 
            "dur": "2.54", 
            "start": "59.795"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "most of which don&#39;t give speeches.", 
            "dur": "2.635", 
            "start": "62.335"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But we have a wise partner", 
            "dur": "1.489", 
            "start": "64.97"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "in the study of freaking out.", 
            "dur": "1.417", 
            "start": "66.459"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Charles Darwin tested fight or flight", 
            "dur": "2.093", 
            "start": "67.876"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "at the London Zoo snake exhibit.", 
            "dur": "2.388", 
            "start": "69.969"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "He wrote in his diary,", 
            "dur": "1.51", 
            "start": "72.357"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;My will and reason were powerless", 
            "dur": "1.067", 
            "start": "73.867"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "against the imagination of a danger", 
            "dur": "1.929", 
            "start": "74.934"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "which had never been experienced.&quot;", 
            "dur": "2.034", 
            "start": "76.863"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "He concluded that his response", 
            "dur": "1.171", 
            "start": "78.897"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "was an ancient reaction unaffected", 
            "dur": "1.825", 
            "start": "80.068"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "by the nuances of modern civilization.", 
            "dur": "2.39", 
            "start": "81.893"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So, to your conscious modern mind,", 
            "dur": "1.456", 
            "start": "84.283"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it&#39;s a speech.", 
            "dur": "1.124", 
            "start": "85.739"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "To the rest of your brain,", 
            "dur": "1.036", 
            "start": "86.863"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "built up to code with the law of the jungle,", 
            "dur": "2.138", 
            "start": "87.899"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "when you perceive the possible consequences", 
            "dur": "1.927", 
            "start": "90.037"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "of blowing a speech,", 
            "dur": "1.019", 
            "start": "91.964"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it&#39;s time to run for your life", 
            "dur": "1.246", 
            "start": "92.983"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "or fight to the death.", 
            "dur": "1.924", 
            "start": "94.229"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Your hypothalamus, common to all vertebrates,", 
            "dur": "2.837", 
            "start": "109.951"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "triggers your pituitary gland to secrete", 
            "dur": "1.944", 
            "start": "112.788"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the hormone ACTH,", 
            "dur": "1.796", 
            "start": "114.732"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "making your adrenal gland", 
            "dur": "1.246", 
            "start": "116.528"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "shoot aadrenaline into your blood.", 
            "dur": "1.954", 
            "start": "117.774"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Your neck and back tense up,", 
            "dur": "2.042", 
            "start": "119.728"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you slouch.", 
            "dur": "0.003", 
            "start": "121.77"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Your legs and hand shake", 
            "dur": "1.343", 
            "start": "121.773"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "as your muscles prepare for attack.", 
            "dur": "1.827", 
            "start": "123.116"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You sweat.", 
            "dur": "0.665", 
            "start": "124.943"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Your blood pressure jumps.", 
            "dur": "1.195", 
            "start": "125.608"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Your digestion shuts down", 
            "dur": "1.489", 
            "start": "126.803"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to maximize the delivery of nutrients", 
            "dur": "1.747", 
            "start": "128.292"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and oxygen to muscles and vital organs,", 
            "dur": "2.461", 
            "start": "130.039"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "so you get dry mouth, butterflies.", 
            "dur": "2.324", 
            "start": "132.5"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Your pupils dilate,", 
            "dur": "1.466", 
            "start": "134.824"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it&#39;s hard to read anything up close,", 
            "dur": "1.811", 
            "start": "136.29"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "like your notes,", 
            "dur": "1.082", 
            "start": "138.101"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but long range is easy.", 
            "dur": "1.602", 
            "start": "139.183"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "That&#39;s how stage fright works.", 
            "dur": "1.719", 
            "start": "140.785"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "How do we fight it?", 
            "dur": "1.286", 
            "start": "142.504"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "First, perspective.", 
            "dur": "2.193", 
            "start": "143.79"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This isn&#39;t all in your head.", 
            "dur": "1.383", 
            "start": "145.983"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s a natural, hormonal, full body reaction", 
            "dur": "2.197", 
            "start": "147.366"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "by an autonomic nervous system on autopilot.", 
            "dur": "2.694", 
            "start": "149.563"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And genetics play a huge role in social anxiety.", 
            "dur": "2.964", 
            "start": "152.257"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "John Lennon played live thousands of times.", 
            "dur": "2.402", 
            "start": "155.221"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Each time he vomited beforehand.", 
            "dur": "2.16", 
            "start": "157.623"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Some people are just wired", 
            "dur": "1.161", 
            "start": "159.783"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to feel more scared performing in public.", 
            "dur": "2.206", 
            "start": "160.944"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Since stage fright is natural and inevitable,", 
            "dur": "2.559", 
            "start": "163.15"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "focus on what you can control.", 
            "dur": "1.733", 
            "start": "165.709"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Practice", 
            "dur": "1.291", 
            "start": "167.442"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "a lot,", 
            "dur": "0.745", 
            "start": "168.733"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "starting long before", 
            "dur": "0.981", 
            "start": "169.478"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "in an environment similar to the real performance.", 
            "dur": "2.851", 
            "start": "170.459"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Practicing any task increases your familiarity", 
            "dur": "2.391", 
            "start": "173.31"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and reduces anxiety,", 
            "dur": "1.5", 
            "start": "175.701"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "so when it&#39;s time to speak in public,", 
            "dur": "1.464", 
            "start": "177.201"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you&#39;re confident in yourself", 
            "dur": "1.166", 
            "start": "178.665"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and the task at hand.", 
            "dur": "1.458", 
            "start": "179.831"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Steve Jobs rehearsed his epic speeches", 
            "dur": "1.621", 
            "start": "181.289"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "for hundreds of hours,", 
            "dur": "1.124", 
            "start": "182.91"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "starting weeks in advance.", 
            "dur": "1.46", 
            "start": "184.034"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "If you know what you&#39;re saying,", 
            "dur": "1.107", 
            "start": "185.494"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you&#39;ll feed off the crowd&#39;s energy", 
            "dur": "1.52", 
            "start": "186.601"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "instead of letting your hypothalamus", 
            "dur": "1.254", 
            "start": "188.121"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "convince your body it&#39;s about to be lunch", 
            "dur": "2.008", 
            "start": "189.375"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "for a pack of predators.", 
            "dur": "1.336", 
            "start": "191.383"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But hey, the vertebrate hypothalamus", 
            "dur": "1.764", 
            "start": "192.719"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "has had millions of years more practice than you.", 
            "dur": "2.792", 
            "start": "194.483"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Just before you go on stage,", 
            "dur": "1.374", 
            "start": "197.275"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it&#39;s time to fight dirty", 
            "dur": "1.478", 
            "start": "198.649"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and trick your brain.", 
            "dur": "1.184", 
            "start": "200.127"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Stretch your arms up and breath deeply.", 
            "dur": "2.346", 
            "start": "201.311"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This makes your hypothalamus trigger", 
            "dur": "1.407", 
            "start": "203.657"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "a relaxation response.", 
            "dur": "1.844", 
            "start": "205.064"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Stage fright usually hits hardest", 
            "dur": "1.542", 
            "start": "206.908"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "right before a presentation,", 
            "dur": "1.45", 
            "start": "208.45"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "so take that last minute to stretch and breathe.", 
            "dur": "2.134", 
            "start": "209.9"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You approach the mic, voice clear,", 
            "dur": "2.01", 
            "start": "212.034"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "body relaxed.", 
            "dur": "1.37", 
            "start": "214.044"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Your well-prepared speech convinces the wild crowd", 
            "dur": "2.625", 
            "start": "215.414"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you&#39;re a charismatic genius.", 
            "dur": "1.997", 
            "start": "218.039"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "How?", 
            "dur": "0.826", 
            "start": "220.036"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You didn&#39;t overcome stage fright,", 
            "dur": "1.408", 
            "start": "220.862"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you adapted to it.", 
            "dur": "1.509", 
            "start": "222.27"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And to the fact that no matter", 
            "dur": "1.074", 
            "start": "223.779"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "how civilized you may seem,", 
            "dur": "1.737", 
            "start": "224.853"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "in part of your brain,", 
            "dur": "0.998", 
            "start": "226.59"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you&#39;re still a wild animal,", 
            "dur": "1.277", 
            "start": "227.588"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "a profound, well-spoken wild animal.", 
            "dur": "3.701", 
            "start": "228.865"
        }
    ], 
